# Supply-chain cooldown: aube refuses to install a dependency version published
# less than this many minutes ago, falling back to the newest version old enough.
# 10080 min = 7 days. Kept numerically aligned with the Dependabot `cooldown`
# (`default-days: 7`) in .github/dependabot.yml so Dependabot only ever proposes
# npm versions aube is willing to install. See the package-manager capability.
minimum-release-age=10080
